<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>LinuxStack Pro Lab</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #0f1117;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: #7AB8E0; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    p  { color: #888; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 800px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #1a1f2e;
      border: 1px solid #2a3560;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover { border-color: #7AB8E0; transform: translateY(-3px); }
    .card h2 { font-size: 1rem; color: #7AB8E0; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .card p  { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>LinuxStack Pro Lab</h1>
  <p>Enterprise Services Stack — Infrastructure de démonstration</p>
  <div class="grid">
    <a class="card" href="/auth/">
      <h2>🔐 Keycloak SSO</h2>
      <p>Gestion des identités</p>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href="https://ipa.{{ domain_name }}/ipa/ui/">
      <h2>📂 FreeIPA</h2>
      <p>Annuaire & DNS</p>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href="/storage/">
      <h2>📁 MinIO</h2>
      <p>Object Storage</p>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href="/monitoring/">
      <h2>📊 Grafana</h2>
      <p>Observabilité & Logs</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
